107
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:17,000
It's not a real existence.

108
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:21,000
We should not think there is a self that's separated from others.

109
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:27,000
We separate ourselves from others because of this body.

110
00:07:27,000 --> 00:07:29,000
But this is an illusion.

111
00:07:29,000 --> 00:07:33,000
We are all together as one phenomenon.

112
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:36,000
But when we see others, we might put up an image.

113
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:40,000
Because we want to impress others or want others to like us.

114
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:42,000
We might be fake nice.

115
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:45,000
But we're not being the genuine self.

116
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:51,000
We're all living in the illusory life of our alaya consciousness.

117
00:07:51,000 --> 00:08:00,000
To understand this, we'll be able to really love and be genuine to all beings and treat everyone like ourselves.

118
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:03,000
The five skandhas, if you open it up,

