00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:41,000
then it becomes the eighteen realms.

125
00:08:41,000 --> 00:08:44,000
The five skandhas, you expand it,

126
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:46,000
it becomes the eighteen realms.

127
00:08:46,000 --> 00:08:48,000
That's our body and mind.

128
00:08:48,000 --> 00:08:52,000
How does it come about to be phenomenon?

