00:08:52,000 --> 00:08:58,000
It's all because of the union and mixture of cause and condition that it exists.

130
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:01,000
It has illusory and false existence.

131
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:08,000
And it's the separation and dispersion of the causation that results in their extinction.

132
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:14,000
All the arising and ceasing, life and death,

133
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:19,000
it's only cause and conditions we call karma.

134
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:25,000
This karma is what's carrying us throughout lifetime, after lifetime.

135
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:27,000
In the sutra, it says,

136
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:30,000
karma, it accords with living beings' minds

137
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:33,000
in response to their capacity to know.

138
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:37,000
Karma is from our own laya consciousness.

139
00:09:37,000 --> 00:09:40,000
It stores all our past karmic deeds.

140
00:09:40,000 --> 00:09:46,000
Right now, we're just experiencing the retribution of our past karmic actions.

141
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:50,000
So our five skandhas up to the eighteen realms

142
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:54,000
is all based on our past karmic deeds.

143
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:58,000
So, for example, there are five members in the family.

