00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:01,000
And love.

146
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:04,000
And one might feel like it's misery.

147
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:06,000
So it's all based on our karma.

148
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:09,000
If we keep ceasing upon conditions,

