168
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:22,000
So that's how they become enlightened.

169
00:11:22,000 --> 00:11:24,000
Through tasting.

170
00:11:24,000 --> 00:11:27,000
The nature of food and tasting

171
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:31,000
is the bright substance of wonderful enlightenment,

172
00:11:31,000 --> 00:11:34,000
our one true mind.

