00:11:34,000 --> 00:11:37,000
Who would have thought that the production,

174
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,000
extinction, coming and going

175
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:43,000
are fundamentally the everlasting wonderful light

176
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:46,000
of the treasury of the Thus Come One,

177
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:49,000
the unmoving, all-pervading perfection

178
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:52,000
and wonderful nature of true suchness.

179
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:56,000
So going back to the Ming meditation,

