00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:05,000
that's talking about all the cause and conditions.

183
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:09,000
They are fundamentally the one true Buddha nature.

184
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:14,000
Here it describes four great qualities of our pure mind.

185
00:12:14,000 --> 00:12:16,000
It's everlasting,

186
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:20,000
which means it doesn't have coming and going.

