00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:48,000
We call it the true suchness.

195
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:51,000
So own up to who you really are.

196
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:54,000
You are not this little bubble,

197
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:56,000
the five skandhas.

198
00:12:56,000 --> 00:13:01,000
We are a big ocean that has infinite potentials.

199
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:06,000
So contemplate the fundamental falseness of appearances

200
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:12,000
and contemplate on the fundamental truth of the nature.

201
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:15,000
All appearances are illusory

202
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:19,000
and the real nature is our one true mind.

